What is your favourite car brand? I have three car brands that I admire; Lexus, Rolls Royce and Lamborghini. Where is your favourite vacation place? My favourite vacation places are California, Turkey and Nigeria. What is your favourite movie? My favourite movies are Judas and the Black Messiah, Game of Thrones and Abeni. What is your favourite song? It is ‘We are the World’ because it is an all-star rendition by my favourite all-time musicians. What is your favourite book? My favourite book is Weep not Child by Ngũgĩ wa Thiong’o. What is your favourite sport? My favourite sport is football and my favourite player is Mbappe. What is your favourite dress style? My favourite dress style is simple and cute. I love it when I dress and people take a second look at me. What is your favourite cologne designer? My favourite cologne is Ralph Lauren. Do you have favourite cloth designers? Yes. I love G and G, Gucci and Burberry. Who is your favourite celebrity? My favourite celebrities are Jide Kosoko, Iya Rainbow, Sola Sobowale and Toyin Abraham. Where is your favourite hangout? I don’t really hang out because of work. But if I have to, I go anywhere nice with my friends. Copyright PUNCH. All rights reserved. This material, and other digital content on this website, may not be reproduced, published, broadcast, rewritten or redistributed in whole or in part without prior express written permission from PUNCH. Contact: theeditor@punchng.com